title: MSB Strengthening Ukraineâ€™s resilience: Mine Action and Rescue Service (MARS)
description: The Swedish Civil Contingencies Agency (MSB, after the Swedish abbreviation) will through this programme support increased Ukrainian resilience and capability to effectively reduce and manage consequences of accidents, emergencies and war. The programme is implemented during 2024 - 2027 and it includes 2 components: 1) Rescue Services and Civil Protection and 2) Mine action. In both components MSB will provide support to relevant Ukrainian government agencies including with equipment and training. Component 1 is also relevant for Ukraine's EU Accession process.
